{"root":{"data":{"id":"djhqcvki16o0","created":1782350037521,"text":"报告与审核审计"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhqdphgxg00","created":1782350102641,"text":"现场检查报告（ON SITE CHECKING REPORT）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":1.9999987185001658,"y":-95.99999856948855}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhqnkx44c00","created":1782350876345,"text":"工厂（Factory）\n报告日期（Report Date）\n检查员（Inspector）\n描述（Description）","layout_right_offset":{"x":26.99999959766876,"y":-10.999999836087397}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhqnz050sg0","created":1782350907004,"text":"A.Description 描述\nB.\nB.1\nB.2\n\nC.Conclusion 结论","layout_right_offset":{"x":30.999999538064117,"y":5.999999910592976}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhra16a5yw0","created":1782352635739,"text":"Coach（word）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-6.74999187141708,"y":48.499999389052505}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrbuhnp8g0","created":1782352777918,"text":"Belt EP Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":63.74999810010212,"y":-59.99999821186083}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrwdu2wlc0","created":1782354387311,"text":"Audited Service Provider\nDate & Time\nAuditor\nTitle\n\nScoring System（\n0：Nothing in place; \n1：Ver basic/simple system in place; \n2:  Comprehensice system in place with scope for considerable improvement \n3:  Good comprehensive system in place that needs fine tuning/perfecting \n4：Very good, comprehensive & up to date system in place\n）\nLogic: Final Result = Rate/Max. Scores (Max.Scores= # of Checking Points ×4)\n\nTable \n\nPart Name\n\nConclusion","layout_right_offset":{"x":127.49999620020412,"y":-8.749999739229736}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhs88c85s80","created":1782355315718,"text":"Table","layout_right_offset":{"x":106.24999683350325,"y":38.74999884515978}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhs8nfuoyw0","created":1782355348589,"text":"1、No.\n2、Description\n3、Using applicators & Processing\n4、Score\n5、Remarks","layout_right_offset":{"x":86.24999742954992,"y":4.999999850988274}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhscx7ukq80","created":1782355683329,"text":"1、Leather Edge Preparation before apply promoter or Edge Paint\n2、Application Process（SOP）\n3、Apply Promoter - UA400H\n4、Apply Primer - CA220R1\n5、Apply Edge Paint - CHS330R1、CHM330R1、DAH630\n6、Drying\n7、Buffing\n8、Polishing\n9、Final appearance\n10、Workers' proficiency\n11、Painted parts before moving to the next production stage","layout_right_offset":{"x":72.49999783933151,"y":174.99999478459375}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhruujgudc0","created":1782354266947,"text":"EP Storage, Prepare and Handling","layout_right_offset":{"x":109.99999672174471,"y":207.49999381601833}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djht1etc29c0","created":1782357602375,"text":"Storage\n\n1、SOP and others guiding for the storage condition is available in Ware house and workshop edge paint storage area\n2、Always keep primer / edge paint at temperature 5℃-30℃ @ 40%-70% Humidity in the warehouse\n3、Keep the Promoter, Primer and Edge Paint away from direct sunlight\n4、Ware house is kept well ventilated\n5、All products must be put on the pallets or shelves for storage\n6、All drums or pails must be closed very well during the storage","layout_right_offset":{"x":183.75003314763262,"y":286.49999479949474}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djht9v2mbug0","created":1782358264677,"text":"Preparation and Handling\n\n1、Preparation should be centralized to ensure consistency\n2、Alaways stirred well in one direction  before handover or distribute to the workers\n3、Cover the drum well and leave it to settle for 30 minutes before handover to the working line\n4、Dispense Primer/Paint into small and clean bottles or stainless basins with cover to distribute to operators\n5、Roller containers without motor should be covered by clear wrap  when not in use or during break\n6、 For all applicators with motor should be kept running during work breaks\n7、Replenish fresh primer or edge paint into inking box for every 30 mins to maintain the viscosity\n8、Never fill ordinary water or mineral water into the primer or edge paint\n9、Never mix Promoter, Primer or Edge Paint together\n10、Do not shake the drum or bottle which will create bubbles\n11、Do not pour the residual promoter, primer or edge paint back to the container of fresh products\n12、All tools used during the application of Edge paint, including brushed, edge paint holders and rollers, should be cleaned with distilled water comletely before leaving or at the end of every shift.\n13、Buffing area is recommended to be arranged far away from the painting area especially the final edge paint application area to ensure for the final appearance\n14、Guiding SOP is available","layout_right_offset":{"x":186.75011185059566,"y":459.8333194073707}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhvu6jbs5s0","created":1782365499135,"text":"Shelf Life and Pot Life\n\n1. Original drums (not yet opened and used) - 6months → Is there any control process available\n2. Original bottles (not yet opened and used) - 6months → Is there any control process available\n3. Well covered inking applicators – 4 hours → Is there any control process available\n4. Closed drums for medium-short term storage(partially used) - 1 month → Is there any control process available\n5. Closed small bottles for short-term storage -1 week → Is there any control process available\n6. Open drums, bottles, inking applicators and other edge painting machines or equipment - 6 months → Is there any control process available\n7. Closed clean small bottles for storage of residual primer or edge paint - 6months → Is there any control process available","layout_right_offset":{"x":143.74999571591616,"y":609.9999818205838}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djht853n0k00","created":1782358129778,"text":"Table\n\n1、Description（No. & Checking Atttibutes）\n2、Demonstration Picture\n3、Actual condition \n4、Scored","layout_right_offset":{"x":193.999994277954,"y":-580.7499862983825}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhwh8yg99c0","created":1782367306779,"text":"Part name\n\n1. Belt with Thickness From 1.5mm to 3mm\n2. Belt with thickness over 3mm","layout_right_offset":{"x":184.99999448657047,"y":-348.74998960644007}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djht19iichs0","created":1782357590835,"text":"Handbag EP Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":191.74999634176504,"y":839.2499824091799}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhscx7ukq80","created":1782355683329,"text":"1、Leather Edge Preparation before apply promoter or Edge Paint\n2、Application Process（SOP）\n3、Apply Promoter - UA400H\n4、Apply Primer - CA220R1\n5、Apply Edge Paint - CHS330R1、CHM330R1、DAH630\n6、Drying\n7、Buffing\n8、Polishing\n9、Final appearance\n10、Workers' proficiency\n11、Painted parts before moving to the next production stage","layout_right_offset":{"x":82.75000420957792,"y":232.49999307096022}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhwhx1qp340","created":1782367359220,"text":"Part Name\n\n1. Long / Short Straight Strap with open ends\n2. Handle or curve long / short strap\n3. Finish Parts:\n- Bag Mouths\n- Gussets\n- Flap Covers\n4. Small components with regular and straight edge:\n- Tabs\n- Panels\n- Zipper collar (Out Side)\n- Other relate parts","layout_right_offset":{"x":101.24999698251474,"y":-309.9999907612805}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhwclwcyh40","created":1782366943130,"text":"Wallet & SLG EP Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":176.24999608844524,"y":1060.749984510243}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhwhx1qp340","created":1782367359220,"text":"Part Name\n\n1. Wallet shell and other functional straight components (such as front/back surface, gusset, flap cover, wristlets) with \nthickness ≈ 2.0-3.5mm\n2. Straight bulk pieces (interior, card slots, ID window) with \nthickness ≤ 1.5mm\n3. Small parts (simple shape such as zipper puller, story patch etc.) with \nthickness ≤ 2.0mm\n4. Small parts (simple shape such as zipper puller, story patch etc.) with \nthickness ≥ 2.0mm\n5. Complex position (anchor, position attached with metal etc.) with \nthickness ≤ 2.0mm\n6. Complex position (anchor, position attached with metal etc.) with \nthickness ≥ 2.0mm","layout_right_offset":{"x":42.00000625848725,"y":-77.49999769032047}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhscx7ukq80","created":1782355683329,"text":"1、Leather Edge Preparation before apply promoter or Edge Paint\n2、Application Process（SOP）\n3、Apply Promoter - UA400H\n4、Apply Primer - CA220R1\n5、Apply Edge Paint - CHS330R1、CHM330R1、DAH630\n6、Drying\n7、Buffing\n8、Polishing\n9、Final appearance\n10、Workers' proficiency\n11、Painted parts before moving to the next production stage","layout_right_offset":{"x":44.000005364417916,"y":23.749999292195014}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhra4ao7eg0","created":1782352642535,"text":"Michael Kors（excel）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":140.33332864112356,"y":230.50010356803182}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrbuhnp8g0","created":1782352777918,"text":"Belt Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":116.2499965354802,"y":564.9999831616883},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-608.7499818578365,"y":863.749974258244}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhy1awex5s0","created":1782371699402,"text":"Components","layout_left_offset":{"x":-267.49999202787876,"y":129.99999612569815},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhx5d86e6g0","created":1782369196814,"text":"For long straight components with two open sides"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhx7tpunk00","created":1782369389439,"text":"Suggested equipment: 2 sides edge painting machine"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhxls3vc1k0","created":1782370483032,"text":"Small parts with curved parts (Anchor / Metal attached position / Punch)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhxmylyunc0","created":1782370575551,"text":"Suggested equipment: Apply by hand with pin"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhx8pzdtps0","created":1782369459673,"text":"1. Proper edge painting procedure\n2. Approiate equipment is used on  components\n3. Rolling speed of the machine is not too fast\n4. Always use the deep-grooves rollers for the application of primer; the fine-frooves rollers for the application of color edge paint\n5. Primer / edge paint must be dry enough before buffing or next application (Use #240 sand paper to sand the surface of the primer lightly, it is dry enough and suitable for next application or buffing if the dust is powder form.)\n6. Drying time is enough according to SOP\n7. Temperature of the drying machine are always set between 40-50℃. Temperature inside the drying machine match the preset temperature withom 5℃\n8. SOPs are shown clearly in each production line\n9. Buffing: Leather flap or wool wheel with good condition\n10.  Emery: emery with #600(or above) emery paper to make it smooth","layout_left_offset":{"x":-293.50000081956387,"y":168.7499949708582}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhxo8o2wnk0","created":1782370675811,"text":"1. Location of sanding and buffing operations: \nLocation of sanding and buffing operation should be far from the location of edge painting operation\n\n2. Keeping track of the temperature and humidity in the production workshop:\nThe temperature and humidity are suitable for edge paint application in the production workshop\n\n3. Applying adhesion promoter:\nAdhesion promoter is used on all components / materials where edge paint would be applied on.\n\n4. Finished / semi-finished products placed:\nThe finished / semi-finished products are placed neatly and not stacked.\n\n5. Leather ironing:\nLeather edge is not ironed before the application of primer.\n\n6. Peeling off test:\nPeeling test machined is operated normally; testing methodology is conducted properly according to MK requirement.\n\n7. Pending time between each coating:\nPending time between each coating (including promoter, primer, and color edge paint) is within 4 hours, or buffing process is proceeded in between if exceeded.","layout_left_offset":{"x":-333.9999836087236,"y":452.4999865144497}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhx4nbah880","created":1782369140406,"text":"Handbag Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":93.7499972060325,"y":606.249981932343},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-587.4999808520085,"y":1585.7499565258627},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhy2jpdk480","created":1782371796932,"text":"Componetnts","layout_left_offset":{"x":-94.24999620765459,"y":-58.74999698251486}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhy2nj58io0","created":1782371805262,"text":"For long straight components with two open sides. (Straps / Handles / Straight & long zipper pulls)","layout_left_offset":{"x":-7.000004783272516,"y":-19.749999649822712}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhy50ei61s0","created":1782371990008,"text":"Suggested equipment: 2 sides edge painting machine ","layout_left_offset":{"x":-39.00000149011589,"y":-14.999999552965164}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhy6n1me4o0","created":1782372117659,"text":"For shorter length component with straight edges (Handles / Story patch / Shell {Cover + Bottom} Panels / Tabs / Finished zipper pulls / Flap edges)","layout_left_offset":{"x":-22.75001598149447,"y":23.749999292194843}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyahivsjc0","created":1782372419099,"text":"Suggested equipment: Inking box with or without motorized roller","layout_left_offset":{"x":-16.500003799796104,"y":-12.49999962747097}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhyb8cpu1k0","created":1782372477499,"text":"Small parts with curve parts. For small componets with irregular shape（Zipper polls / Hang tags）","layout_left_offset":{"x":-67.49999798834347,"y":87.49999739229679}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhye8p2ts80","created":1782372713339,"text":"Suggested equipment: small roller inking box"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhyftkysts0","created":1782372837167,"text":"Small parts with curved parts. (Anchor / Metal attached position / Punch)","layout_left_offset":{"x":-42.25000204890989,"y":168.74999497085787}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyge4ypew0","created":1782372881912,"text":"Suggested equipment: apply by hand with pin","layout_left_offset":{"x":8.749999739229679,"y":-14.999999552965392}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhxo8o2wnk0","created":1782370675811,"text":"1. Location of sanding and buffing operations: \nLocation of sanding and buffing operation should be far from the location of edge painting operation\n\n2. Keeping track of the temperature and humidity in the production workshop:\nThe temperature and humidity are suitable for edge paint application in the production workshop\n\n3. Applying adhesion promoter:\nAdhesion promoter is used on all components / materials where edge paint would be applied on.\n\n4. Finished / semi-finished products placed:\nThe finished / semi-finished products are placed neatly and not stacked.\n\n5. Leather ironing:\nLeather edge is not ironed before the application of primer.\n\n6. Peeling off test:\nPeeling test machined is operated normally; testing methodology is conducted properly according to MK requirement.\n\n7. Pending time between each coating:\nPending time between each coating (including promoter, primer, and color edge paint) is within 4 hours, or buffing process is proceeded in between if exceeded.","layout_left_offset":{"x":-325.2499838694939,"y":223.7499933317307}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhx4sy28xc0","created":1782369152667,"text":"Storage","layout_right_offset":{"x":83.74999750405561,"y":657.4999804049739},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-211.2499937042598,"y":3196.2499047443293}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhywy4kor40","created":1782374179251,"text":"1. Preparation of primer and edge paint should be centralized to ensure consistency.\n\n2. Keep products away from the floor and putting on the pallets or shelves.\n\n3. Always keep the products away from direct sunlight and well ventilated in the warehouse.\n\n4. Always track the temperature and humidity with thermometer and hygrometer, and keep the primer and edge paint at the temperature 25-35℃ / Humidity 60 - 70% in the warehouse.\n\n5. Always use auto mixer or a stick to stir the whole drum of primer and edge paint well in one direction before using. The stirring time should be at least 5 min.\n\n6. Cover the drum well when not using in the warehouse\n\n7. All primer and edge paint are kept within expiry date\n\n8. Dispense primer / edge paint into small and clean small bottles or stainless basins with well covered and distrubute to operators.\n\n9. Inking boxes (without electrical motors) should be covered and put into sealed plastic bag (or covered with a wet towel) when not in use or during the break.\n\n10. For all applicators with electrical motor should be kept running or cleaned during the break.","layout_left_offset":{"x":-248.24997269362308,"y":136.2499975785613}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhynpfbe6o0","created":1782373455032,"text":"Wallet Application","layout_left_offset":{"x":-158.74999526888166,"y":2013.7499399855744},"layout_right_offset":{"x":-255.9999961853025,"y":371.99999445676804}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyodi27kg0","created":1782373507441,"text":"Components","layout_left_offset":{"x":-82.49999754130863,"y":-48.749998547136784}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyokz32ao0","created":1782373523707,"text":"For components that have been treated with \nlamination. (Finished wallets / interior / surface / gusset / partition top / inner top)\n ","layout_left_offset":{"x":-171.49999649822712,"y":-69.99999791383743}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyr0eyjk80","created":1782373714047,"text":"Suggested equipment: Inking box with or without motorized roller","layout_left_offset":{"x":-102.00000432133675,"y":-18.749999441206455}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhysajwf9c0","created":1782373814478,"text":"For shorter length component with straight \nedges (Wristlet / Story patch / Shell panels flap / Tabs / Finished zipper pulls / Flap edges)\n ","layout_left_offset":{"x":-192.99998375773475,"y":-27.499999180436134}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyr0eyjk80","created":1782373714047,"text":"Suggested equipment: Inking box with or without motorized roller","layout_left_offset":{"x":-102.00000432133675,"y":-18.749999441206455}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhyt4yx1xc0","created":1782373880690,"text":"Small parts with curve parts. For small components with irregular shape. (Zipper pulls / Hang tags)","layout_left_offset":{"x":-184.4999987334013,"y":34.999998956918716}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyr0eyjk80","created":1782373714047,"text":"Suggested equipment: Small roller inking box","layout_left_offset":{"x":-102.00000432133675,"y":-18.749999441206455}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhyuh5vtkg0","created":1782373985596,"text":"Small parts with curved parts. (Anchor / Metal attached position / Punch)","layout_left_offset":{"x":-273.7499918416146,"y":82.4999975413084}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhyr0eyjk80","created":1782373714047,"text":"Suggested equipment: Apply by hand with pin","layout_left_offset":{"x":-102.00000432133675,"y":-18.749999441206455}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhxo8o2wnk0","created":1782370675811,"text":"1. Location of sanding and buffing operations: \nLocation of sanding and buffing operation should be far from the location of edge painting operation\n\n2. Keeping track of the temperature and humidity in the production workshop:\nThe temperature and humidity are suitable for edge paint application in the production workshop\n\n3. Applying adhesion promoter:\nAdhesion promoter is used on all components / materials where edge paint would be applied on.\n\n4. Finished / semi-finished products placed:\nThe finished / semi-finished products are placed neatly and not stacked.\n\n5. Leather ironing:\nLeather edge is not ironed before the application of primer.\n\n6. Peeling off test:\nPeeling test machined is operated normally; testing methodology is conducted properly according to MK requirement.\n\n7. Pending time between each coating:\nPending time between each coating (including promoter, primer, and color edge paint) is within 4 hours, or buffing process is proceeded in between if exceeded.","layout_left_offset":{"x":-387.24999489635275,"y":182.49999798834358}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhwur766mo0","created":1782368365222,"text":"Audit date\nService provider audited\nAudited for\nAudited by\n\nScoring System:\n  *Overall rating = Score / Max Score X 100%\n   *N.A. = Process Not Applicable in the factory\n   **Critical category highlighted in orange\n   **Major category highlighted in yellow\n   **Minor category not highlighted\n  0: Serious Concern\n   1: Attention needed\n   2: Fair\n   3: Good\n\nTable\n\nIssues found with suggested corrective actions","layout_right_offset":{"x":76.24999772757292,"y":-207.4999938160181},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-568.7499830499299,"y":-437.4999869614844}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhwxota1340","created":1782368595121,"text":"Table\n\n1. No.\n2. Checking Categories\n3. Checking Attributes\n4. Inspected scores (Score - Max Score)\n5. Comments","layout_right_offset":{"x":98.74999705702078,"y":-122.49999634921596},"layout_left_offset":{"x":-302.49999098479793,"y":204.99999389052425}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djiqwsc2kcw0","created":1782453157721,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhrb3uhoe80","created":1782352719921,"text":"Tory Burch（excel）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":161.49998809397243,"y":3964.4999212175626}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrpeoysts0","created":1782353840630,"text":"Handbag Application\nStorage\nWallet Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":32.49999903142452,"y":-36.2499989196657}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}